Lines: 敵は、予想以上に内部まで浸透しているようだ。
DeepL_mtl: The enemy seems to have penetrated further into the interior than expected.

Lines: 地下水脈を使って侵入した、工作隊の存在が
DeepL_mtl: It seems that the presence of an operative team, which used underground water veins to infiltrate the site, was significant.

Lines: 指揮系統が混乱してないのが救いだな。
DeepL_mtl: Thank God the chain of command isn't in disarray.

Lines: 新米パイロットたちじゃ、やっぱりジオンの相手は
DeepL_mtl: It seems that the new pilots can't take on Zion after all.

Lines: 俺たちは、本部施設の護衛をしつつ、同区画の敵を排除する。
DeepL_mtl: We'll be escorting the headquarters facility while eliminating the enemy in the same section.

Lines: そういえば、さっきのアムロくんとの会話の時から、「俺」とか
DeepL_mtl: Come to think of it, you've been saying "I" since your conversation with Mr. Amuro earlier, haven't you?

Lines: 正規部隊だって頼りになるってとこを見せてやらなきゃ、
彼は頑張りすぎで、危なっかしいんだよ…。
DeepL_mtl: Don't make fun of me, Lil.
We have to show him that even regular troops can be relied on, he's trying too hard, he's in danger...

Lines: ガラじゃないけど、そのほうが、ずっと「らしい」わよ？
アラン隊長。　フフフ…。
DeepL_mtl: It's not a gala, but it's much more "typical" that way, no? Captain Alan.

Lines: ほ、ほら！　時間がないぞ！
DeepL_mtl: Oh, look!　We're running out of time! Unit 1, relaunch!
